comment: Meeting to discuss hiring a salesman for CRM sales.
description: The meeting held on the 10th of December, 2024, included attendees Yassar Bouchentouf, Ashraf Nashash, Hamza Koutar, and Louis Young. The primary topic was the need to hire a salesman to sell the company's CRM product. Discussions covered the sales strategy, which emphasized a targeted approach to acquiring qualified leads. It was also mentioned that GenHive company would be one of the first clients for this sales initiative.
